snippet.title: Pawball | A VR Soccer Game with Cats! | ALPHA Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Pawball is a Cat vs Cat VR Soccer Game. Use your hands to run, climb, jump and "kick" the ball in this multiplayer game developed by ARVORE Immersive

Currently in ALPHA
Early Access coming in June 2024

For more PAWBALL content check our social media
